@startuml
title Authentication Process

actor User
participant UI
control AuthController
database UsersDB

User -> UI : Enter credentials
activate User
activate UI

UI -> AuthController : Login(username, password)
activate AuthController

AuthController -> UsersDB : SELECT user
activate UsersDB
UsersDB --> AuthController : User data
deactivate UsersDB

alt User found
    AuthController --> UI : Success + token
    UI --> User : Welcome!
else User not found
    AuthController --> UI : Error
    UI --> User : Invalid credentials
end

deactivate AuthController
deactivate UI
deactivate User
@enduml